{
  "text": "The result of the current study with Dixon's up-and-down method suggested that the dose of remifentanil 0.2-0.3 \u03bcg/kg with 1 mg/kg of propofol provided excellent LMA insertion in elderly patients. The dose of remifentanil from this result was somewhat less than the expected value considering that less propofol (1 mg/kg) was used compared with those with adults (2.5 mg/kg) of the previous investigations [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
